business_rules_view_code:
create or replace view business_rules.release_s_psa_c_release as
select 
    bo."bk component",       -- business key for hub component
    bo."bk release",         -- business key for hub release
    bo."product name",       -- product_name from satellite release > psa > main
    bo."release guid",       -- release_guid from satellite release > psa > main
    bo."release version"     -- release_version from satellite release > psa > main

  from businessobjects.release_s_psa_c_release bo
;
